OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Nino Cerruti - one of the great Italian
OL,6, designers and fashion entrepreneurs -  
OL,7, has died aged 91.                      
OL,9,FReports say he passed away in hospital 
OL,10,Fin Piedmont where he had checked in for
OL,11,Fa hip operation.                       
OL,13,FHe always insisted on trying on his own
OL,14,Fcreations first. Many of them were kept
OL,15,Fat the textile factory his grandfather 
OL,16,Ffounded in the northern town of Biella 
OL,17,Fin 1881.                               
OL,19,F"I have always dressed the same person,
OL,20,Fmyself," he once said, according to AFP
OL,21,Fnews agency.                           
